						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up in the temple of Vemalamma.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. It gives a long list of number of Brāhmaṇas of various <hi rend="italic">gōtras</hi> and records the gift of one <hi rend="italic">tūmu</hi> of land to god Bētēśvaradēva on the orders of the <hi rend="italic">Mahājanas.</hi> In characters of the 13th century A.D.</p>						

